## Problem Statement

Given an integer `N`, print a pattern where the `i-th` row contains the number `i` repeated `i` times.

### Example

Input:
N = 5

Output:
1
22
333
4444
55555


CODE:
class Solution {
public:
    void pattern4(int n) {
        for(int i = 1 ; i<=n ; i++){
            for(int j = 0 ; j<=i ; j++){
                cout<<i;
            }
            cout<<endl;
        }

    }
};

TIME COMPLEXITY - O(N^2)
SPACE COMPLEXITY - O(1)
